{
  "chapter": 77,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述花无缺与魏黄衣的生死对决，魏黄衣虽被花无缺杀死，但其临死前的疯狂令人唏嘘。铁心兰与花无缺在客栈中坦诚相待，解开了彼此的心结，铁心兰表示只想将花无缺当作兄长，两人关系更加坦荡。随后二人在街头面摊偶遇神秘黑衣人，此人自称是江小鱼的朋友，却透露出赴死之意，留下金珠后独自离去。花无缺察觉黑衣人将有危险，决定追踪前往一座庙宇道观，发现后院藏有猛虎与黄幔，危机四伏，为下一章埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_huang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏黄衣",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，我知道你在哪里，你逃不了的，今日你我两人谁也休想活着走，我要和你一起死在这里！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在不忍和你动手，我劝你还是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_huang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏黄衣",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我用不着你可怜我，我……我就算找不到你，也用不着你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_wei_huang_yi",
      "text": "你快走吧，我知道花……花公子绝不会阻拦你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_huang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏黄衣",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "走？……你难道不知道无牙门下，可杀不可辱……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_huang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏黄衣",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你不该多话的，我虽杀不了花无缺，却能杀死你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_huang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏黄衣",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我要死，至少也得有一个人陪着我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我本不忍杀他的，我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我错了，我本不该多嘴的，否则你也不必勉强自己来杀一个没有眼睛的人，我……我为什么总是会把事情弄得一团糟。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你认为你错了么？你只不过是心太软了。错，并不在你，你本想将每件事都做好的，你已尽了你的力量了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你总是对我这么好，而我……我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无牙门下，好厉害的无牙门下，江小鱼，你对付得了么？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无牙门下的弟子，已如此厉害，何况魏无牙自己？江小鱼呀江小鱼，我实在难免要替你担心。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "江小鱼，他难道已经……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "他此刻只怕已到了龟山，只怕已快见着魏无牙了！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "门没有关，进来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我……我睡不着，心里有几句话，想来对你说。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "请坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我知道这些日子来，你故意很冷淡我，很疏远我。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你要我说真话？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "迟早总要说的话，为什么不现在说？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你知道，人与人之间在一起接近得久了，就难免要生出感情，尤其是在困苦与患难中。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我不是怕你对不起他，而是怕我自己，我……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我不忍把你的情感拖入矛盾里，假如我和你接近得太多，不但我痛苦，你也会痛苦。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但我……我是个孤苦的女孩子，我只想把你当做我真的兄长，我希望你能相信我……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我此刻只是要告诉你，你不必疏远我，也不必防范我。只要我们心里光明坦荡，就不怕对不起别人，也不必怕别人的想法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我现在才知道你很有勇气，这勇气，平常虽看不出，但到了必要时，你却比任何人都勇敢得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我把这些话说出来，心里真的愉快多了，我真想喝杯酒庆祝庆祝。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我心里也痛快多了，我也正想喝杯酒庆祝庆祝。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "坐在这种小面摊上喝酒，倒也别有风味，却不知道你嫌不嫌脏？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你真的把我看成只肯坐在高楼上喝酒的那种人么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我们切半斤牛肉，来一斤酒。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "如此良宵，有酒有肉，这本已足够了，但我却总还觉得缺少了什么，现在我才知道缺少的是什么了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你是说……缺少一个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "没有他在一起，你我岂能尽欢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你想，我们三个人会不会有在一起喝酒的时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "为什么不会有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "来，你我且为江小鱼干一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你就是花无缺？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "正是，阁下……？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你就是铁心兰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你们方才可是为江小鱼干了一杯？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好！你们为江小鱼干一杯，我最少要敬你们三杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "喝呀！你们难道怕酒中有毒不成？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "对不起，我们没有和陌生人喝酒的习惯，你若要敬我们的酒，至少总得先说出你是谁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你也莫管我是谁，只要知道我是江小鱼的朋友就好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "好，你既是江小鱼的朋友，我就喝了这一杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "在下喝三杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，你很好，很够朋友。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你在这样的星光下，和这样的美女坐在一起喝酒，心里居然还没有忘记江小鱼，好……好……我再敬你三杯！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "你真的和江小鱼是朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "江小鱼又不是什么了不起的大人物，我为何要冒认是他朋友？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你们若是瞧见他时，不妨代我向他问好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "我们见着小鱼儿时，说你是谁呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你就说是他大哥好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我不是刚告诉你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "放屁，小鱼儿绝不会认别人是他大哥的，你休想骗我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好，好，你们当真不愧是小鱼儿的知己——不错，我一心想要他叫我一声大哥，但他却总是要叫我兄弟。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "喂，我看你像是有什么心事？是么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "心事？我会有什么心事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "text": "你若真将我们当成江小鱼的朋友，为何不将心事说出来，也许……也许我们能帮你的忙。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "帮忙！我难道会要别人帮忙！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，你们就每人敬我三杯酒吧，这就算帮了我的忙了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我本当今夜只有一个人独自度过，谁知竟遇着了你们，陪我痛饮了一夜，这也算是我人生一大快事了……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nan",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是给你的酒钱，全给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "在他临死前的晚上，他本都以为要独自度过的，他竟找不到一个朋友来陪他度过最后的一天。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "临死的晚上？最后一天？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你还瞧不出么？……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我去追他，你在这里等着。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你跟我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你怎知他已快死了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "他随时在留意着时刻，显见他今天晚上一定有件要紧的事要去做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这我也发觉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "但他既是江小鱼的朋友，我们又怎能坐视他去送死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他轻功已是顶尖好手，就算打不过别人，也该能跑得了的，但却完全不抱能逃走的希望，他那对头，岂非可怕得很？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "所以你要分外小心，有我在，你千万不要随意出手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他难道就是到这道观里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "他进去时，行动甚为小心，以他的轻功，别人暂时必定难以觉察，所以我就先赶回去找你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你在这里等着，我进去看看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我看这其中必定还有些蹊跷，说不定这也是他和别人串通好的陷阱，故意要将我们诱到这里来的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "此人若是真的要诱我入伏，我更要瞧个究竟了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到这人的脾气有时竟也和小鱼儿一模一样。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 357
    }
  ],
